<body>

    <h1>Non-Vegetarian Diet Plan for Weight Loss</h1>

    <div class="guidelines">
        <h2>General Guidelines</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Caloric Deficit:</strong> Aim to consume fewer calories than you burn.</li>
            <li><strong>Nutrient-Dense Foods:</strong> Focus on whole, minimally processed foods.</li>
            <li><strong>Hydration:</strong> Drink plenty of water, aiming for at least 8 cups a day.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="meal-plan">
        <h2>Sample Meal Plan</h2>

        <h3>Breakfast</h3>
        <p>Omelette made with 2-3 eggs, spinach, and tomatoes<br>A slice of whole grain toast</p>

        <h3>Morning Snack</h3>
        <p>Greek yogurt (low-fat) with a handful of berries</p>

        <h3>Lunch</h3>
        <p>Grilled chicken breast with a large mixed green salad (lettuce, cucumbers, tomatoes) topped with olive oil and vinegar</p>

        <h3>Afternoon Snack</h3>
        <p>Sliced turkey or chicken breast wrapped in lettuce</p>

        <h3>Dinner</h3>
        <p>Baked fish (like salmon or tilapia) with steamed broccoli and quinoa</p>

        <h3>Evening Snack (optional)</h3>
        <p>Cottage cheese with a sprinkle of cinnamon and a few slices of fruit</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
